THIRD-PARTY SOFTWARE NOTICES AND INFORMATION

This project uses the following third-party libraries and components:

1. Tokio (MIT License)

   - https://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio
   - Asynchronous runtime for Rust

2. Axum (MIT License)

   - https://github.com/tokio-rs/axum
   - Web framework for Rust

3. Prometheus Client (Apache-2.0 OR MIT)

   - https://github.com/prometheus/client_rust
   - Prometheus metrics library

4. Serde (MIT OR Apache-2.0)

   - https://github.com/serde-rs/serde
   - Serialization framework

5. Tracing (MIT License)

   - https://github.com/tokio-rs/tracing
   - Application-level tracing framework

6. Thiserror (MIT OR Apache-2.0)

   - https://github.com/dtolnay/thiserror
   - Error handling library

7. MD5 (Apache-2.0/MIT)

   - https://github.com/RustCrypto/hashes
   - MD5 hash implementation (used for RouterOS authentication)

8. Dotenvy (MIT License)
   - https://github.com/allan2/dotenvy
   - .env file support

For a complete list of dependencies and their licenses, run:
cargo tree --prefix none --format "{p} {l}"

================================================================================

PROTOCOL IMPLEMENTATION

This project implements the MikroTik RouterOS API protocol based on the
publicly documented specifications available in the official MikroTik
documentation:

- https://wiki.mikrotik.com/wiki/Manual:API

The protocol implementation in src/mikrotik/connection.rs is an original work
written specifically for this project and does not contain code copied from
other implementations.

